        </span>
        <span class="hero-badge inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-emerald-500/20 backdrop-blur-md border border-emerald-400/30 text-emerald-200 text-sm font-medium px-4 py-2 rounded-full" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;">
