          🛒 E-Commerce
        </span>
        <span class="hero-badge inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-pink-500/20 backdrop-blur-md border border-pink-400/30 text-pink-200 text-sm font-medium px-4 py-2 rounded-full" style="animation-delay: 1.5s;">
          🎨 Branding
        </span>
